0above%20you%2C%20you%20feel%20a%20sense%20of%20security%20that%20it's%20hard%20to%20convey%20in%20words%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20former%20Army%20Green%20Beret%20officer%2C%20granted%20anonymity%20because%20of%20their%20current%20work%20with%20the%20US%20government%2C%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Air%20Force%20has%20operated%20six%20versions%20of%20the%20gunship%20%E2%80%94%20AC-130A%2C%20AC-130E%2C%20AC-130H%2C%20AC-130U%2C%20AC130W%2C%20and%20AC-130J%20%E2%80%94%20during%20its%20five%20decades%20in%20service.%20The%20AC-130J%20is%20armed%20with%2030%20mm%20and%20105%20mm%20cannons%20and%20can%20fire%20a%20plethora%20of%20smart%20munitions%2C%20including%20the%20GBU-39%20Small%20Diameter%20Bomb%2C%20GBU-69%20Small%20Glide%20Munition%2C%20AGM-114%20Hellfire%20missiles%2C%20and%20AGM-176%20Griffin%20missiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22AC-130J%20Australia%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e64a76912f290019a9c965%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221331%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20US%20Air%20Force%20crew%20chief%20marshals%20an%20AC-130J%20at%20Royal%20Australian%20Air%20Force%20Base%20Richmond%20during%20Talisman%20Sabre%20in%20July.%3Cp%3EUS%20Air%20Force%2FAirman%201st%20Class%20Tylir%20Meyer%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20AC-130%20will%20face%20new%20challenges%20in%20a%20conflict%20against%20a%20capable%20adversary.%20The%20complete%20air%20superiority%20the%20US%20military%20enjoyed%20in%20the%20wars%20in%20Iraq%20and%20Afghanistan%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffighter-jets-unable-to-provide-close-air-support-over-ukraine-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_top%5C%22%3Ewon't%20be%20there%20in%20a%20war%20with%20Russia%20or%20China%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20the%20Air%20Force%20will%20have%20to%20find%20ways%20to%20keep%20the%20AC-130%20relevant%20in%20non-permissive%20or%20semi-perm