s%20wanting%20to%20join%20as%20partner%20countries%20of%20BRICS%20(Brazil%2C%20Russia%2C%20India%2C%20China%20and%20South%20Africa).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20remarks%2C%20South%20Africa%20President%20Cyril%20Ramaphosa%20announced%20the%20outcomes%20of%20the%2015th%20BRICS%20Summit%20and%20said%20the%20grouping%20will%20be%20expanded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20reached%20an%20agreement%20to%20invite%20Argentina%2C%20Egypt%2C%20Ethiopia%2C%20Iran%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%20and%20UAE%20to%20become%20full%20members%20of%20BRICS.%20The%20membership%20will%20come%20into%20effect%20from%20January%202024%2C%26quot%3B%20Ramaphosa%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParticipating%20in%20the%20BRICS%20Summit%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20PM%20Modi%20had%20said%20India%20fully%20supports%20the%20expansion%20of%20the%20BRICS%20membership%20and%20welcomes%20moving%20forward%20with%20consensus%20in%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%202016%2C%20during%20India's%20chairmanship%2C%20we%20defined%20BRICS%20as%20Building%20Responsive%2C%20Inclusive%2C%20and%20Collective%20Solutions.%20After%20seven%20years%2C%20we%20can%20say%20that%20BRICS%20will%20be%20%E2%80%93%20Breaking%20barriers%2C%20Revitalizing%20economies%2C%20Inspiring%20Innovation%2C%20Creating%20opportunities%2C%20and%20Shaping%20the%20future.%20Together%20with%20all%20the%20BRICS%20partners%2C%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20contribute%20actively%20in%20making%20this%20new%20definition%20meaningful%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692871740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F12arktm8_modi-xi-1200_625x300_24_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-xi-jinping-shake-hands-greet-each-other-at-brics-4325263%22%2C%22summary