udy-2023-2%23%3A~%3Atext%3DChatGPT%2520may%2520be%2520the%2520fastest%252Dgrowing%2520app%2520in%2520history%2520with%2Ceasy%2520access%2520and%2520faster%2520responses.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Efastest-growing%20consumer%20AI%20application%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20ever%20this%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20research%2C%20conducted%20by%20Kai-Cheng%20Yang%2C%20a%20computational%20social%20science%20researcher%2C%20and%20Filippo%20Menczer%2C%20a%20computer-science%20professor%2C%20found%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feverything-you-need-to-know-about-chat-gpt-2023-1%23%3A~%3Atext%3DChatbots%2520like%2520ChatGPT%2520are%2520powered%2Calso%2520understand%2520words%2520in%2520context.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EChatGPT%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E's%20ability%20to%20generate%20authoritative-looking%20text%20is%20being%20used%20to%20run%20%26quot%3Bbotnets%26quot%3B%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhat%20are%20botnets%20and%20why%20are%20they%20bad%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBotnets%20are%20networks%20of%20hundreds%20of%20harmful%20bots%20and%20spam%20campaigns%20on%20social%20media%20that%20can%20go%20undetected%20by%20current%20anti-spam%20filters.%20They%20are%20deployed%20for%20many%20reasons%20%E2%80%94%20in%20this%20case%2C%20the%20botnets%20are%20promoting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcrypto-scams-conned-thousands-collective-1-billion-ftc-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Efraudulent%20cryptocurrencies%20and%20NFTs%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bot%20accounts%20attempt%20to%20convince%20people%20to%20invest%20in%20fake%20cryptocurrencies%20and%20may%20even%20steal%20from%20their%20existing%20crypto%20wallets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20network%20Yang%20and%20Menczer%20discovered%20on%20X%20housed%20over%201%2C000%20active%20bots.%20The%20bots%20followed%20and%20responded%20to%20each%20other's%20posts%20with%20ChatGPT%20outputs%2C%20often%20publishing%20selfies%20stolen%20from%20human%20profiles%20to%20build%20fake%20personas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rise%20of%20social%20media%20gave%20bad%20actors%20a%20cheap%20way%20to%20reach%20a%20large%20audience%20and%20monetize%20false%20or%20misleading%20content%2C%20Menczer%20said.%20New%20AI%20tools%20%26quot%3Bfurther%20lower%20the%20cost%20to%20generate%20false%20but%20credible%20content%20at%20scale%2C%20defeating%20the%20already%20weak%20moderation%20defenses%20of%20social-media%20platforms%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftwitter-bots-comprise-less-than-5-but-tweet-more-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esocial-media%20bots%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0accounts%20that%20are%20wholly%20or%20partly%20controlled%20by%20software%20%E2%80%94%20have%20been%20routinely%20deployed%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffortune.com%2F2023%2F03%2F06%2Ftwitter-bot-network-uncovered-pro-trump-against-nikki-haley-ron-desantis%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eamplify%20misinformation%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20events%2C%20from%20elections%20to%20public-health%20crises%20such%20as%20COVID.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20social-media%20bots%20have%20been%20easy%20to%20pick%20out%20because%20of%20their%20robotic%20behavior%20and%20unconvincing%20fake%20personas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20generative-AI%20tools%20like%20ChatGPT%20produce%20humanlike%20text%20and%20media%20in%20seconds.%20%26quot%3BThe%20advancement%20of%20AI%20tools%20will%20distort%20the%20idea%20of%20online%20information%20permanently%2C%26quot%3B%20Yang%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20bots%20in%20the%20network%20uncovered%20by%20the%20researchers%20mainly%20posted%20about%20fraudulent%20crypto%20and%20NFT%20campaigns%20and%20promoted%20suspicious%20websites%20on%20similar%20topics%2C%20which%20themselves%20were%20likely%20written%20with%20ChatGPT%2C%20the%20survey%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EEntire%20websites%20can%20be%20made%20up%20of%20AI-generated%20misinformation%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20social%20media%2C%20ChatGPT-like%20tools%20have%20generated%20spammy%20generic%20news%20websites%2C%20many%20of%20which%20publish%20blatant%20falsehoods.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fnewsguardtech.com%2Fspecial-reports%2Fai-tracking-center%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ENewsGuard%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20private%20company%20that%20rates%20news%20and%20information%20websites'%20reliability%2C%20has%20so%20far%20found%20more%20than%20400%20such%20AI-generated%20websites%20as%20part%20of%20its%20ongoing%20audits%20since%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20websites%20generate%20advertising%20revenue%20from%20automated%20ad%20tech%20that%20purchases%20ad%20space%20on%20websites%20regardless%20of%20their%20quality%20or%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWe%20can%20still%20detect%20AI-generated%20spam%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0for%20now%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20NewsGuard%20and%20the%20paper's%20researchers%20were%20separately%20able%20to%20unearth%20AI-generated%20spam%20content%20using%20an%20obvious%20tell%20that%20chatbots%20currently%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20ChatGPT%20can't%20produce%20an%20answer%20because%20the%20prompt%20is%20against%20OpenAI's%20policies%20or%20concerns%20private%20information%2C%20it%20generates%20a%20canned%20response%20such%20as%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20sorry%2C%20but%20I%20cannot%20comply%20with%20this%20request.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearchers%20look%20for%20when%20these%20responses%20slip%20out%20in%20an%20automated%20bot's%20content%2C%20whether%20on%20a%20webpage%20or%20in%20a%20tweet.%20They%20use%20the%20phrases%20to%20uncover%20parts%20of%20a%20broader%20bot%20campaign%20and%20from%20there%20discover%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20spam%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20experts%20fear%20that%20as%20chatbots%20get%20better%20at%20mimicking%20humans%2C%20such%20telltale%20signs%20will%20disappear%20and%20make%20it%20much%20harder%20to%20track%20AI-generated%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWei%20Xu%2C%20a%20computer-science%20professor%20at%20the%20Georgia%20Institute%20of%20Technology%2C%20told%20Insider%20that%20it%20will%20become%20harder%20to%20detect%20and%20filter%20AI-generated%20content%20while%20more%20malicious%20users%20exploit%20it%2C%20creating%20a%20vicious%20cycle%20of%20AI-generated%20content%20that's%20increasingly%20hard%20to%20detect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EXu's%20concerns%20could%20be%20a%20reality%20soon.%20Europol%2C%20the%20EU's%20law-enforcement%20agency%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Ffuturism.com%2Fthe-byte%2Fexperts-90-online-content-ai-generated%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Epredicts%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2090%25%20of%20internet%20content%20will%20be%20AI-generated%20by%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithout%20regulation%2C%20as%20long%20as%20there%20are%20more%20incentives%20and%20low%20costs%20for%20creating%20AI-generated%20content%2C%20bad%20actors%20will%20always%20be%20far%20ahead%20of%20those%20trying%20to%20shut%20it%20down%2C%20added%20Xu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20similar%20to%20plastic%20bottled%20water.%20We%20know%20it%20is%20a%20disaster%20for%20the%20environment%2C%20but%20as%20long%20as%20it%20is%20cheap%20without%20a%20big%20penalty%2C%20it%20will%20widely%20exist%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Xu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ERegulators%20are%20sprinting%20to%20catch%20up%20with%20the%20deluge%20of%20spam%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20content%20detectors%20available%2C%20such%20as%20ZeroGPT%20and%20the%20OpenAI%20AI%20Text%20Classifier%2C%20are%20unreliable%20and%20often%20can't%20accurately%20tell%20the%20difference%20between%20human-generated%20and%20AI-generated%20content%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farxiv.org%2Fftp%2Farxiv%2Fpapers%2F2306%2F2306.15666.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Erecent%20study%20by%20European%20academics%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20found.%20OpenAI's%20de