0associated%20with%20each%20one.%20When%20someone%20sends%20an%20ice-cream%20cone%2C%20I%20say%2C%20%26quot%3Bmm%2C%20ice%20cream%20so%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20has%20become%20my%20most%20famous%20catchphrase.%20My%20favorite%20one%20to%20say%20is%20%26quot%3Byee-haw%2C%20yes%2C%20got%20me%20feeling%20like%20a%20cowgirl.%26quot%3B%20It's%20just%20so%20fun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spend%20about%20six%20hours%20a%20day%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-make-money-livestreaming%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edoing%20livestreams%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20making%20content.%20My%20other%20videos%20bring%20in%20a%20little%20income%2C%20but%20nowhere%20near%20as%20much%20as%20my%20NPC%20livestreams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20like%20a%20full-time%20job.%20I%20don't%20get%20tired%20while%20doing%20it%20because%20I%20see%20the%20views%20going%20up%2C%20and%20all%20the%20gifts%20I'm%20getting%20make%20me%20energetic.%20I%20get%20lost%20playing%20as%20my%20NPC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20know%20that%20some%20people%20think%20this%20is%20fetish%20content%2C%20but%20that's%20not%20why%20I%20started%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20just%20looking%20for%20something%20new%20I%20could%20do%20on%20TikTok%2C%20and%20there%20are%20even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnewsroom.tiktok.com%2Fcommunity-guidelines%3Flang%3Dmr%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Erules%20on%20the%20platform%20about%20how%20sexual%20you%20can%20be%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20honestly%2C%20if%20people%20want%20to%20consider%20it%20fetish%20content%2C%20that's%20fine%20by%20me.%20They're%20only%20saying%20that%20because%20I%20have%20a%20great%20body%20and%20I%20look%20great%2C%20so%20people%20consider%20it%20a%20fetish.%20I'm%20getting%20paid%20either%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithin%20my%201.1%20million%20followers%2C%20I%20even%20have%20celebrity%20fans.%20At%20one%20point%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F07%2F17%2Fstyle%2Fpi