%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-brics-22-countries-expansion-stakes%5C%22%3EAs%20BRICS%20Evolves%20Criteria%20for%20Expansion%2C%20Here%E2%80%99s%20What%20India%20Thinks%20of%20the%2022%20Countries%20That%20Want%20to%20Join%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20official%20sources%20said%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20objective%20during%20the%20negotiations%20was%20to%20give%20first%20preference%20to%20its%20%E2%80%9CStrategic%20Partners%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOut%20of%20the%20six%20countries%20invited%20to%20join%20BRICS%2C%20India%20has%20a%20strategic%20partnership%20with%20five%3A%20Argentina%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20Iran%2C%20UAE%20and%20Egypt.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENote%3A%20This%20is%20a%20developing%20story%20and%20details%20will%20be%20added%20as%20they%20become%20available.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692867752000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F24142824%2FScreenshot-2023-08-24-at-2.26.56-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fbrics-expansion-finalised-as-egypt-iran-ethiopia-argentina-saudi-and-uae-invited-to-join%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Out%20of%20the%20six%20countries%20invited%20to%20join%20the%20bloc%2C%20New%20Delhi%20has%20a%20strategic%20partnership%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0to%20whom%20Indian%20official%20sources%20said%20first%20preference%20would%20be%20given%20%E2%80%93%20with%20all%20but%20Ethiopia.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fbrics-expansion-finalised-as-egypt-iran-ethiopia-argentina-saudi-and-uae-invited-to-join%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20PM%20Modi%2C%20Xi%20Jinping's%20Brief%20Interaction%20At%20BRICS%20Summit%20In%20S%20Africa%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp