%20and%20in%20online%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20improved%20leaps%20and%20bounds%20and%20with%20the%20work%20put%20in%20under%20noted%20coach%20R%20B%20Ramesh%20and%20subsequently%20Anand%20(as%20the%20mentor)%2C%20Praggnanandhaa%20can%20only%20get%20better%2C%20which%20may%20not%20be%20good%20news%20for%20his%20rivals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20achieved%20a%20lot%20at%2018%20and%20is%20already%20on%20the%20path%20to%20greatness.%20With%20people%20of%20the%20stature%20of%20Anand%20and%20Ramesh%20to%20guide%20him%2C%20the%20Chennai%20player%20will%20be%20dreaming%20of%20becoming%20the%20world%20champion%20sooner%20than%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20someone%20so%20talented%2C%20Praggnanandhaa%2C%20surprisingly%2C%20is%20yet%20to%20win%20the%20national%20championship%20despite%20his%20other%20accomplishments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20performance%20in%20the%20FIDE%20World%20Cup%20has%20turned%20the%20spotlight%20firmly%20on%20him%20even%20as%20compatriots%20like%20D%20Gukesh%20and%20Arjun%20Erigaisi%20too%20has%20kept%20reminding%20the%20chess%20world%20of%20their%20own%20potential.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20triumph%20against%20Carlsen%20would%20certainly%20help%20Praggnanandhaa%20pull%20away%20from%20the%20two%20ambitious%20fellow%20Indians%20and%20on%20the%20way%20to%20achieving%20his%20dream%20of%20fighting%20for%20the%20world%20title%20by%20contesting%20the%20Candidates%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692865140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fasa1opeo_r-praggnanandhaa_625x300_22_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fchess%2Fr-praggnanandhaa-not-just-a-wonderkid-but-a-great-in-the-making-4324904%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20stunning%20performance%20in%20the%20FIDE%20World%20Cup%20in%20B