3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcab-crashes-into-wall-of-minister-kiren-rijijus-home-leaves-gaping-hole-4325028%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explained%3A%20The%20Accusations%20In%20Rakhi%20Sawant%20Vs%20Adil%20Durrani%20Drama%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fsearch%3Fsearchtext%3DRakhi-Sawant%5C%22%3EActress%20Rakhi%20Sawant%20%3C%2Fa%3Eis%20in%20the%20news%20for%20all%20the%20wrong%20reasons%2C%20yet%20again.%20Over%20the%20last%20several%20days%2C%20her%20soured%20equation%20with%20estranged%20husband%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fsearch%3Fsearchtext%3DAdil-Khan-Durrani-%5C%22%3EAdil%20Khan%20Durrani%20%3C%2Fa%3Ehas%20played%20out%20in%20the%20public%20eye%20much%20like%20an%20over-the-top%20daily%20soap.%20There%20have%20been%20accusations%20of%20violence%20and%20cheating%20from%20both%20sides%20and%20Adil%20Durrani%2C%20a%20businessman%2C%20even%20spent%20a%20considerable%20time%20in%20jail%20after%20Rakhi%20Sawant%20filed%20a%20few%20cases%20against%20him.%20Upon%20being%20released%2C%20Adil%20Durrani%20approached%20the%20media%20and%20stirred%20up%20the%20proverbial%20hornet's%20nest%20with%20a%20bunch%20of%20allegations%20about%20the%20actress%2C%20including%20claims%20that%20she%20was%20also%20already%20married%20to%20one%20Ritesh%20Singh%20when%20she%20exchanged%20vows%C2%A0with%C2%A0Adil%20Durrani.%20Adil%20Durrani's%20interview%20and%20press%20conference%20was%20countered%20by%20Rakhi%20Sawant's%20own%20press%20meeting.%20This%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20led%20to%20another%20bunch%20of%20interviews%20where%20Adil%20Durrani%20shared%20more%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20issue%20at%20a%20glance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20making%20their%20relationship%20public%20in%202022%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Frakhi-sawant-rubbishes-adil-durranis-claim-that-she-cannot-get-pregnant-4319374%5C%22%3ERakhi%20Sawant%20and%20Adil%20Khan%20Durrani%20%3C%2Fa%3Eannounced%20their%20wedding%20in%20January%202023.%20When%20Rakhi%20accused%20Adil%20Khan%20Durrani%20of%20domestic%20violence%20and%20cheating%2C%20it%20was%20revealed%20that%20Rakhi%20and%20Adil%20have%20been%20married%20since%20May%202022.%C2%A0%20In%20February%202023%2C%20Rakhi%20filed%20an%20FIR%20against%20Adil%20Durrani%20under%20sections%20406%20420%2C%20498%20%5BA%5D%20and%20377%20of%20the%20IPC.%20Adil%20was%20subsequently%20arrested%20and%20released%20on%20bail%20after%20spending%20nearly%20five%20months%20in%20Mysuru%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%C2%A0let%20us%20take%20a%20look%20at%20some%20of%20the%20allegations%20that%20the%20estranged%20partners%20have%20levelled%20at%20each%20other%20and%20the%20clarifications%20that%20followed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Adil%20Khan%20accuses%20Rakhi%20Sawant%20of%20falsely%20framing%20him%20in%20cases%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20In%20his%20press%20conference%2C%20Adil%20Khan%20Durrani%20alleged%20that%20Rakhi%20Sawant%20has%20falsely%20implicated%20him%20in%20cases%20that%20led%20to%20his%20arrest.%20Instead%2C%20he%20alleged%20that%20it%20was%20Rakhi%20Sawant%20who%20hit%20him%20and%20cheated%20him%20during%20the%20course%20of%20their%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20shared%20that%20the%20rape%20charges%20levelled%20at%20him%20by%20an%20Irani%20woman%20were%20also%20done%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20Rakhi%20Sawant%2C%20who%20Adil%20claims%20paid%20the%20complainant%20money%20to%20press%20false%20charges.%20He%20said%20that%20he%20had%20briefly%20known%20the%20complainant%20and%20rescued%20her%20financially.%20He%20also%20denied%20any%20sort%20of%20sexual%20intercourse%20with%20the%20woman.%20%26quot%3BShe%20%5BRakhi%20Sawant%5D%20gave%20that%20Irani%20girl%20Rs%203%20lakh%20in%20cash%20and%20promised%20to%20make%20her%20a%20star.%20She%20even%20told%20her%20they%20could%20extract%C2%A0%20Rs%2025%20to%2030%20lakhs%20from%20me.%20She%20took%20help%20from%20her%20and%20went%20to%20Mysore%20police%20station%20to%20lodge%20an%20FIR%20against%20me%20for%20rape.%20She%20said%20that%20she%20knows%20me%20for%205%20years%20and%20I%20raped%20her%20one-and-a-half%20years%20ago.%20Why%20did%20she%20wait%20so%20long%20to%20complain%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20the%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERakhi%20Sawant's%20clarification%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20actress%20meanwhile%20shared%20that%20Adil%20Durrani%20spent%20only%2022%20days%20in%20jail%20on%20account%20of%20her%20complaint.%20The%20rest%2C%20she%20said%2C%20was%20due%20to%20the%20rape%20case.%20She%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EKya%20duniya%20ko%20itna%20nahi%20pata%20ki%20woh%20jo%206%20mahina%20jail%20mein%20rehkar%20aaye%20woh%20Rakhi%20Sawant%20ke%20liye%20nahi%20rahe%3F%20Unki%20Irani%20girlfriend%20ne%20waha%20pe%20unpe%20rape%20ka%20case%20lagaya%20hai.%20Mere%20liye%20nahi%20rahe%20hai%20woh.%20Mere%20liye%20yaha%2022%20din%20the%20jo%20mujhe%20mara%20tha%2C%20mujhe%20torture%20kiya%20tha%3C%2Fem%3E%20((Is%20everybody%20not%20aware%20that%20the%20last%20few%20months%20that%20he%20was%20in%20jail%20wasn't%20because%20of%20Rakhi%20Sawant%3F%20His%20Irani%20girlfriend%20filed%20a%20rape%20case%20against%20him%20there.%20He%20wasn't%20there%20because%20of%20me.%20For%20me%2C%20he%20was%20in%20jail%20for%2022%20days%20because%20he%20beat%20me%20up%2C%20and%20tortured%20me.%20I%20saw%20him%20having%20sex%20with%20other%20girls%2C%20with%20men%20too%2C%20in%20my%20house.%20He%20tried%20to%20beat%20me%20in%20Dubai%2C%20here%20too.%20I%20was%20silent.)%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Rakhi%20Sawant%20accuses%20Adil%20Durrani%20of%20rape%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIn%20her%20press%20conference%2C%20Rakhi%20Sawant%20has%20accused%20Adil%20Durrani%20of%20raping%20her%20and%20recording%20her%20nude%20images.%20Adding%20that%20she%20met%20Adil%20through%20a%20friend%20Shelly%20on%20the%20pretext%20of%20getting%20a%20car%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20told%20Shelly%20to%20send%20the%20car%20to%20Mumbai%20but%20Adil%20insisted%20that%20I%20come%20to%20Mysuru.%20He%20had%20made%20a%20plan%20to%20trap%20me.%20I%20took%20my%20brother%20Rajiv%20with%20me.%20I%20had%20asked%20Adil%20to%20book%20two%20rooms%20but%20he%20made%20sure%20they%20were%20apart.%20Adil%20came%20to%20my%20room.%20Somebody%20he%20knew%20came%20there%20and%20locked%20us%20from%20outside.%20And%20I%20shouldn't%20tell%20you%20more.%20There%20are%20three%20witnesses%20to%20this%20-%20Uorfi%20Javed%2C%20Shelly%20and%20Rajeev.%20It%20took%20him%20three%20hours%20to%20tear%20my%20clothes.%20I%20decided%20to%20go%20to%20the%20police%20station%20and%20file%20a%20complaint.%20I%20called%20Uorfi%20and%20asked%20her%20what%20to%20do.%20She%20was%20my%20best%20friend%20then.%20She%20said%2C%20'I%20will%20send%20you%20a%20car%2C%20you%20come%2C%20we%20will%20get%20your%20hotel%20changed...Adil%20said%2C%20'Don't%20be%20sad%2C%20you%20are%20a%20nice%20girl%2C%20I%20want%20to%20marry%20you%20and%20live%20with%20you'.%20It%20changed%20my%20heart.%E2%80%9D%20Adil%20Durrani%20has%20denied%20the%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%C2%A0Rakhi%20Sawant%20accuses%20Adil%20Durrani%20of%20selling%20her%20nude%20videos%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20the%20press%20conference%2C%20Rakhi%20Sawant%20also%20accused%C2%A0Adil%20Durrani%20of%20recording%20and%20selling%C2%A0her%20nude%20videos%20for%C2%A0Rs%2047%20lakh.%20Speaking%20about%20the%20videos%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20in%20the%20bathroom%20and%20he's%20shootin%3Cem%3Eg.%20Aise%20bohot%20saare%20videos.%20Mera%20full%20body%20nude%20dikh%20rahe%20hai.%20I%20was%20quiet.%20I%20was%20his%20wife%20and%20he%20was%20raping%20me%20in%20the%20house.%20Videos%20viral%20ho%20jayenga%20na%20fir%20kya%20karu%20main.%20Zaher%20kha%20jau%2C%20suicide%20kar%20lu%2C%20kaha%20jau%3F%20Pure%20duniya%20mere%20nude%20video%20dekhne%20ke%20baad%20kaha%20jau%3F%20Kidhar%20jau%2C%20kaunse%20samaj%20mein%20rahu%3F%20Tell%20me%20where%20should%20I%20go%3F%20How%20to%20show%20my%20face%20to%20the%20world%3F%20Mai%20normal%20ladki%20nehi%20hu%2C%20India%20ke%20celebrity%20hu%2C%20ek%20brand%20hu.%20Within%20one-year%20mera%20talaq%20kar%20diya%20use.%3C%2Fem%3E%20(What%20will%20I%20do%20if%20my%20videos%20go%20viral%3F%20Should%20I%20consume%20poison%20and%20die%3F%20Where%20will%20I%20go%20if%20the%20whole%20world%20sees%20my%20nude%20images%3F)%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dpnb7wYEWGGA%5C%22%3Eshe%20told%20Pinkvilla.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdil%20Durrani's%20clarification%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIn%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGMDrccWpJpU%26pp%3DygUQc2lkZGhhcnRoIGthbm5hbg%253D%253D%5C%22%3Einterview%20with%20Siddharth%20Kannan%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3EAdil%20Durrani%20denied%20all%20the%20rape%20charges%20and%20also%20said%20that%20explicit%20content%20featuring%20Rakhi%20Sawant%20has%20been%20available%20online%20for%20years%20now.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CRakhi%20Sawant%20is%20extremely%20interested%20in%20recording%20nude%20videos%E2%80%A6She%20created%20a%20group%20%E2%80%9CRakhi%20Sawant%20Important%20Updates%E2%80%9D%20on%20February%209%20after%20I%20was%20arrested%20on%20February%207.%20In%20the%20group%2C%20she%20has%20shared%20nude%20videos%20that%20she%20has%20recorded%20of%20me%E2%80%A6She%20shared%20the%20content%20in%20the%20group%20with%20paparazzi%20members%E2%80%A6I%20also%20have%20a%20pen%20drive%20to%20show%20when%20these%20nude%20videos%20were%20deleted%20by%20Rakhi%20Sawant%20in%20the%20group%E2%80%A6She%20wanted%20members%20of%20the%20media%20to%20share%20the%20videos%20and%20announce%20that%20Adil%20has%20sold%20the%20videos%20for%20Rs%2047%20lakh.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Adil%20Durrani%20accuses%20Rakhi%20Sawant%20of%20being%20married%20to%20Ritesh%20Singh%3A%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20businessman%20accused%20the%20actress%20of%20cheating%20on%20him%20and%20lying%20to%20him%20about%20getting%20divorced%20from%20her%20previous%20husband%2C%20Ritesh%20Singh.%20He%20also%20shared%20that%20Rakhi%20and%20Ritesh%20were%20pursuing%20an%20illicit%20relationship%20in%20London.%20In%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DocffY_eeoGk%5C%22%3Einterview%20with%20Bollywood%20Bubble%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20Adil%20Durrani%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20in%20Dubai.%20She%20comes%20back%20normally.%20Her%20phone%20used%20to%20be%20with%20me%2C%20mine%20with%20her.%20I%2C%20one%20day%2C%20saw%20some%20messages.%20%3Cem%3EAur%20wo%20itne%20gande%20thay%20just%20imagine%20mujhe%20kya%20feel%20hua%20hoga.%20Wo%20bolti%20hai%20Ritesh%20%5BSingh%5D%20maine%20galti%20karli%20hai%20Adil%20se%20shaadi%20karke%20tum%20meri%20jaan%20ho.%20Mere%207%20din%20aapke%20saath%20bahut%20ache%20rahe%20hai%2C%20main%20bhul%20nahi%20sakti.%20Aur%20jo%20bhi%20tumhare%20saath%20hua%20wo%20memories%20mujhe%20yaad%20aagaye%20hai.%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5BOne%20day%20I%20saw%20some%20vulgar%20messages%20on%20her%20phone.%20She%20was%20telling%20Ritesh%20%5BSingh%5D%20that%20she%20regrets%20getting%20married%20to%20me.%20I%20will%20always%20cherish%20the%20memories%20we%20made%20during%20these%20seven%20days.%5D%20How%20should%20I%20feel%3F%20I%20was%20like%20%3Cem%3Eye%20kya%20ho%20raha%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%5BWhat%20is%20happening%3F%5D%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERakhi%20Sawant's%20clarification%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20When%20asked%20about%20why%20she%20introduced%20Ritesh%20Singh%20as%20her%20husband%20on%20%3Cem%3EBigg%20Boss%3C%2Fem%3E%20a%20few%20years%20ago%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYes%2C%20I%20introduced%20Ritesh%20as%20my%20husband%20in%20%3Cem%3EBigg%20Boss%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20but%20later%20I%20got%20to%20know%20that%20he%20hadn't%20divorced%20his%20wife%2C%20so%20our%20marriage%20was%20null%20and%20void.%20I%20used%20to%20keep%20in%20touch%20with%20Ritesh%20through%20messages%20occasionally%2C%20but%20I%20never%20met%20him%20after%20I%20married%20Adil%20in%20May%202022.%20Adil%20is%20lying%20that%20I%20continued%20to%20meet%20Ritesh.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERakhi%20Sawant%20during%20her%20press%20conference%20also%20called%20Ritesh%20Singh%20to%20share%20his%20thoughts.%20Over%20a%20video%20call%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMy%20first%20question%20is%20why%20is%20the%20video%20not%20with%20the%20police.%20He%20is%20trying%20to%20create%20a%20scandal%20by%20speaking%20to%20the%20media.%20How%20Rakhi%20and%20I%20met%20is%20already%20known.%20He%20smartly%20used%20everything%20against%20Rakhi%2C%20he%20has%20intentionally%20used%20things%20against%20Rakhi.%20It%20was%20a%20plan%20set%20by%20him%20to%20gain%20publicity%20and%20become%20famous.%20Rakhi%20was%20very%20loyal%20to%20him.%20I%20am%20in%20support%20of%20her.%20She%20is%20a%20friend%2C%20is%20loyal%20and%20speaks%20the%20truth.%26quot%3B%20He%20also%20clarified%20that%20he%20wasn't%20in%20London%20when%20Rakhi%20visited%20the%20country.%20He%20showed%20his%20passport%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdil%20Durrani's%20counterclaim%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAdil%20Durrani%20pointed%20out%20that%20it%20is%20possible%20to%20travel%20from%20Greece%20to%20London%20via%20train%20or%20by%20road.%20In%20some%20cases%2C%20a%20separate%20visa%20is%20not%20required%20to%20travel%20to%20London%20from%20Greece%2C%20so%20Ritesh%20Singh%20showing%20his%20passport%20proves%20nothing%2C%20Adil%20Durrani%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Adil%20Durrani%20accuses%20Rakhi%20Sawant%20of%20domestic%20violence%2C%20financial%20exploitation%3A%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAdil%20accused%20Rakhi%20of%20beating%20him%20brutally%20whenever%20he%20tried%20talking%20to%20her%20about%20their%20personal%20issues.%20He%20also%20alleged%20that%20she%20had%20misused%20his%20finances%20and%20that%20she%20owed%20him%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERakhi%20Sawant's%20version%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20actress%20said%20that%20A