ch%20is%20a%20procedural%20test%2C%20is%20done%20in%20rape%20cases%20to%20ascertain%20if%20the%20accused%20is%20capable%20of%20engaging%20in%20sexual%20acts%2C%20a%20surgical%20manual%20examination%20is%20carried%20out%20to%20confirm%20if%20the%20vasectomy%20was%20done%20or%20not.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20semen%20analysis%20is%20carried%20out%20to%20check%20for%20fertility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20said%20that%20the%20victim%E2%80%99s%20statement%20was%20recorded%20as%20per%20Section%20164%20of%20the%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%20(CrPC)%20to%20verify%20her%20allegations%20as%20well%20as%20to%20know%20the%20sequence%20of%20events.%20The%20minor%20is%20being%20counselled%2C%20the%20officer%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%2C%20Premoday%20Khakha%2C%20an%20official%20in%20the%20Delhi%20government%E2%80%99s%20Women%20and%20Child%20Development%20(WCD)%20department%2C%20was%20sent%20to%20a%2014-day%20judicial%20custody%20along%20with%20his%20wife%20Seema%20Rani%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20August%2023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%2C%20the%20girl%20began%20to%20live%20with%20the%20accused%2C%20whom%20she%20referred%20to%20as%20uncle%2C%20following%20the%20death%20of%20her%20father.%20The%20girl%20said%20that%20she%20moved%20along%20with%20her%20mother%20to%20live%20with%20her%20uncle%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20as%20they%20were%20%E2%80%9Cdepressed%E2%80%9D%20due%20to%20her%20father%E2%80%99s%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20went%20to%20my%20uncle%E2%80%99s%20house%20after%20the%20(father%E2%80%99s)%20death%20to%20divert%20my%20mind%20and%20started%20attending%20online%20classes%20from%20there.%20From%20November%202020%20to%20January%202021%2C%20uncle%20raped%20me%E2%80%A6%20aunty%20was%20strict%20and%20would%20hit%20me%20when%20I%20would%20score%20less%20marks.%20The%20last%20time%20he%20sexually%20assaulted%20me%20was%20in%20January%202021%20and%20then%20I%20missed%20my%20period.%20Aunty%20said%20that%20they%20will%20get%20an%20abortion%20done%20since%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20first%20month%E2%80%A6%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20tell%20my%20mother%20anything%2C%20thinking%20she%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20believe%20(me).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20coming%20days%2C%20the%20police%20will%20question%20the%20family%20of%20the%20accused%20and%20their%20friends%20and%20neighbours.%20The%20police%20so%20far%20have%20prepared%20a%20list%20of%2010%20witnesses%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692862152000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F24125734%2FSandeep-Mahajan-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmultiple-medical-tests-conducted-on-delhi-govt-official-accused-of-rape-of-minor-girl%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20accused%2C%20Premoday%20Khakha%2C%20an%20official%20in%20the%20Delhi%20government's%20Women%20and%20Child%20Development%20department%2C%20said%20he%20had%20got%20a%20vasectomy%20in%202005.%20He%20has%20been%20made%20to%20take%20several%20tests%20following%20his%20claim.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmultiple-medical-tests-conducted-on-delhi-govt-official-accused-of-rape-of-minor-girl%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Indian%20American%20Vivek%20Ramaswamy%20Clapped%20Back%20On%20Barack%20Obama%20Dig%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndian%20American%20Vivek%20Ramaswamy%20appeared%20to%20outdo%20weathered%20rivals%20at%20the%20first%20Republican%20presidential%20debate%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20taking%20the%20most%20potshots%20and%20even%20clapping%20back%20in%20equal%20measure.%20One%20of%20the%20highlights%20of%20his%20debate%20debut%20was%20a%20comparison%20with%20former%20US%20President%20Barack%20Obama%2C%20provoked%20by%20his%20own%20introduction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVivek%20Ramaswamy%2C%2038%2C%20was%20described%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Bamateur%26quot%3B%20Barack%20Obama%20by%20fellow%20aspirant%20Chris%20Christie%2C%20former%20New%20Jersey%20Governor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20jibe%20was%20linked%20to%20Vivek%20Ramaswamy%20describing%20himself%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bskinny%20guy%20with%20a%20funny%20last%20name%26quot%3B%2C%20reminding%20many%20of%20the%20former%20US%20President.%20He%20has%20even%20been%20slammed%20on%20social%20media%20for%20%26quot%3Bplagiarising%20Obama%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet%20me%20just%20address%20the%20question%20that%20is%20on%20everybody's%20mind%20at%20home%20tonight.%20Who%20the%20heck%20is%20this%20skinny%20guy%20with%20a%20funny%20last%20name%2C%20and%20what%20the%20heck%20is%20he%20doing%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20this%20debate%20stage%3F%26quot%3B%20said%20Vivek%20Ramaswamy%2C%20grinning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'll%20tell%20you%2C%20I'm%20not%20a%20politician.%20You're%20right%20about%20that.%20I'm%20an%20entrepreneur.%20My%20parents%20came%20to%20this%20country%20with%20no%20money%2040%20years%20ago.%20I%20have%20gone%20on%20to%20found%20multi-billion%20dollar%20companies.%20That%20is%20the%20American%20dream.%20And%20I%20am%20genuinely%20worried%20that%20that%20American%20dream%20will%20not%20exist%20for%20our%20two%20sons%20and%20their%20generation%20unless%20we%20do%20something%20about%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20during%20the%20debate%2C%20Chris%20Christie%20referred%20to%20the%20comment%20as%20he%20growled%3A%20%26quot%3BHold%20on%2C%20I've%20had%20enough%20already%20tonight%20of%20a%20guy%20who%20sounds%20like%20ChatGPT.%26quot%3B%20He%20was%20reacted%20to%20Mr%20Ramaswamy's%20comment%20that%20the%20climate%20change%20agenda%20is%20a%20hoax.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20stands%20up%20here%2C%20and%20the%20last%20person%20in%20one%20of%20these%20debates%2C%20Brett%2C%20who%20stood%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20stage%20and%20said%2C%20'What's%20a%20skinny%20guy%20with%20an%20odd%20last%20name%20doing%20up%20here'%20was%20Barack%20Obama.%20And%20I'm%20afraid%20we're%20dealing%20with%20the%20same%20type%20of%20amateur%20tendencies%20tonight%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Christie%2C%2060.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ramaswamy%20shot%20back%3A%20%26quot%3BGive%20me%20a%20hug%20like%20you%20did%20to%20Obama%2C%20and%20you'll%20help%20elect%20me%20just%20like%20you%20did%20to%20Obama.%20Give%20me%20the%20damn%20hug%2C%20brother.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202012%2C%20Chris%20Christie%20faced%20criticism%20for%20apparently%20hugging%20Obama%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20Hurricane%20Sandy%2C%20days%20before%20the%202012%20presidential%20election.%20Mr%20Christie%20denied%20that%20he%20had%20ever%20done%20so.%20%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20hug%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Republican%20insisted%2C%20and%20stuck%20to%20it%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpinion%20polls%20show%20Mr%20Ramaswamy%20ranking%20second%20after%20former%20US%20president%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20who%20skipped%20the%20debate%20yesterday%20but%20still%20grabbed%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ramaswamy%2C%20who%20has%20been%20moving%20up%20the%20charts%20over%20the%20past%20few%20weeks%2C%20elbowing%20other%20presidential%20aspirants%20in%20his%20party%2C%20was%20also%20repeatedly%20attacked%20by%20former%20Vice%20President%20Mike%20Pence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20need%20to%20bring%20in%20a%20rookie%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pence%20said%2C%20pointing%20at%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20reacted%20to%20Mr%20Ramaswamy's%20comment%20on%20climate%20change.%20%26quot%3BClimate%20change%20is%20real%2C%20by%20the%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20president%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20Mr%20Ramaswamy%2C%20the%20other%20Indian-American%20on%20the%20Republican%20presidential%20debate%20stage%20was%20former%20South%20Carolina%20Governor%20Nikki%20Haley%2C%20the%20only%20woman%20in%20the%20race%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20was%20Mr%20Ramaswamy%20who%20was%20at%20the%20receiving%20end%20of%20most%20attacks%20during%20the%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Barack%20Obama%20comparisons%2C%20Indian-American%20Congressman%20Ro%20Khanna%20posted%20that%20the%20former%20US%20President%20Obama%20%26quot%3Bmust%20be%20smiling%26quot%3B%20somewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSomewhere%20%40BarackObama%20must%20be%20smiling%20that%20a%2038-year-old%20son%20of%20Hindu%20immigrants%20running%20to%20the%20right%20of%20Trump%20is%20cribbing%20from%20him!%20Obama's%20vision%20for%20a%20multiracial%20democracy%20is%20seeping%20into%20our%20politics%20despite%20the%20intense%20backlash.%20A%20slow%20but%20satisfying%20vindication%2C%26quot%3B%20Ro%20Khanna%20posted%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ramaswamy%2C%20a%20second-generation%20Indian-American%2C%20founded%20Roivant%20Sciences%20in%202014%20and%20led%20the%20largest%20biotech%20IPOs%20of%202015%20and%202016%2C%20according%20to%20his%20bio.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692861840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F6jgbfcqo_vivek-ramaswamy-afp-_625x300_24_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-indian-american-vivek-ramaswamy-clapped-back-on-barack-obama-dig-4324918%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian%20American%20Vivek%20Ramaswamy%20appeared%20to%20outdo%20weathered%20rivals%20at%20the%20first%20Republican%20presidential%20debate%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20taking%20the%20most%20potshots%20and%20even%20clapping%20back%20in%20equal%20measure.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-indian-american-vivek-ramaswamy-clapped-back-on-barack-obama-dig-4324918%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-indian-american-vivek-ramaswamy-clapped-back-on-barack-obama-dig-432491