E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20job%20drives%20are%20being%20held%20once%20a%20month%20from%20October%202022%2C%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20addressing%20each%20of%20these%20events%20virtually.%20Appointment%20letters%20are%20given%20away%20to%20%E2%80%98fresh%20job%20takers%E2%80%99%2C%20according%20to%20the%20government.%20These%20monthly%20events%20are%20held%20simultaneously%20in%2045%20cities%2C%20with%20a%20publicity%20overdrive%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20government%20to%20counter%20criticism%20that%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20has%20failed%20miserably%20in%20creating%20jobs%20for%20the%20youth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20received%20from%20the%20government%2C%20in%20response%20to%20information%20sought%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20under%20the%20Right%20to%20Information%20(RTI)%2C%20has%20revealed%20that%20even%20promotions%20are%20being%20passed%20off%20as%20new%20recruitments%20and%20are%20being%20added%20to%20the%20cumulative%20data%20to%20inflate%20the%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Science%20Education%20and%20Research%20(IISER)%2C%20Mohali%2C%20in%20April%20this%20year%2C%20made%2015%20new%20appointments%20and%20approved%2021%20promotions.%20Letters%20to%20the%20newly%20appointed%20persons%20as%20well%20as%20those%20who%20received%20promotions%20at%20IISET%2C%20however%2C%20were%20issued%20letters%20during%20the%20Rozgar%20Mela%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%2038%20persons%20were%20given%20appointment%20letters%20for%20positions%20at%20the%20Maulana%20Azad%20National%20Urdu%20University%20in%20April.%20However%2C%20the%20fine%20print%20reveals%20that%2018%20out%20of%20these%20were%20mere%20cases%20of%20promotions%2C%20not%20new%20employment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20outlet%20sought%20a%20response%20from%20Union%20higher%20education%20secretary%2C%20Sanjay%20Murthy%2C%20on%20the%20rationale%20behind%20including%20promotions%20in%20the%20newly%20generated%20employment%20data.%20However%2C%20he%20is%20yet%20to%20respond.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20getting%20promotions%20are%20already%20in%20service.%20Their%20position%20only%20changes.%20There%20is%20no%20logic%20to%20consider%20them%20as%20fresh%20employment.%20Inclusion%20of%20promotion%20data%20helps%20the%20government%20to%20create%20some%20records%20but%20it%20is%20misleading%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20faculty%20member%20at%20an%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20(IIT)%20told%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20these%3Cem%3E%20melas%3C%2Fem%3E%20are%20not%20really%20in%20line%20with%20the%20publicised%20objectives%2C%20a%20meticulously%20planned%20publicity%20drive%2C%20however%2C%20is%20in%20place%20before%20and%20after%20these%20events%20every%20month.%20Public%20broadcasters%20Doordarshan%20and%20All%20Indian%20Radio%20along%20with%20government-run%20Press%20Information%20Bureau%20are%20roped%20in%20to%20ensure%20maximum%20visibility.%20Protocols%20further%20say%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20speeches%20should%20be%20telecast%20live%20on%20giant%20screens%20at%20these%20melas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Department%20of%20Personnel%20and%20Training%20(DoPT)%2C%20which%20is%20the%20nodal%20agency%20for%20this%2C%20records%20sound%20bites%20of%20newly%20appointed%20recruits%20in%20high%20resolution%2C%20who%20mention%20their%20names%20and%20their%20job%20offers%20in%20these%20videos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJob%20creation%20is%20crucial%20for%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20who%20will%20be%20seeking%20a%20third%20term%20in%20office%20in%20May%202024.%20His%20nine-year%20term%20is%20criticised%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Findias-workforce-not-rising-quality-of-jobs-very-low-cmies-mahesh-vyas%5C%22%3Ehighest%20joblessness%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20country%20has%20seen%20in%20the%20last%20few%20decades.%20There%20is%20a%20perceptible%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Findia-narendra-modi-jobs-unemployment%5C%22%3Ediscontent%3C%2Fa%3E%20among%20the%20youth%20over%20the%20lack%20of%20jobs%20and%20low%20wages.%20Although%20the%20unemployment%20rate%20fell%20in%20July%20%E2%80%93%20as%20it%20does%20during%20this%20time%20of%20year%20due%20to%20sowing%20season%20%E2%80%93%20it%20still%20remains%20at%20a%20staggering%207.95%25%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Findia-s-unemployment-rate-falls-in-july-due-to-farm-demand-1243145.html%5C%22%3Edata%3C%2Fa%3E%20released%20by%20the%20Centre%20for%20Monitoring%20Indian%20Economy%20(CMIE).%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692857169000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F18123649%2F8554011101_6fa66ae66f_c.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpromotions-are-also-being-passed-off-as-new-jobs-to-inflate-figures-of-rozgar-melas-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22These%20job%20drives%20are%20being%20held%20once%20a%20month%20from%20October%202022%2C%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20addressing%20each%20of%20these%20events%20virtually.%20Appointment%20letters%20are%20given%20away%20to%20'fresh%20job%20takers'%2C%20according%20to%20the%20government.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpromotions-are-also-being-passed-off-as-new-jobs-to-inflate-figures-of-rozgar-melas-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mamata's%20statement%20on%20Roshan%20Sr%20sparks%20meme%20fest%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692856675000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103009715%2Cimgsize-38034.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fchandrayaan-3-internet-churns-out-hilarious-memes-on-mamata-banerjees-statement-on-when-rakesh-roshan-landed-