0Year%E2%80%99s%20Eve%20in%202002%20that%20proved%20to%20be%20the%20turning%20point%20of%20their%20story.%20Intent%20on%20helping%20their%20friends%20find%20a%20getaway%20where%20they%20could%20ring%20in%20the%20new%20year%20in%20style%2C%20Susmitha%20and%20Shreedev%20offered%20them%20their%20very%20own%20recently-revamped%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20days%20that%20the%20couple%E2%80%99s%20friends%20spent%20at%20Woodway%20were%20the%20loveliest%2C%20to%20say%20the%20least.%20This%20was%20encouraging%20news%20for%20the%20couple%20who%20had%20long%20since%20ruminated%20on%20the%20idea%20of%20welcoming%20guests%20into%20the%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Woodway%20Heritage%20Bungalow%20is%20almost%20always%20booked%20to%20capacity%20and%20those%20who%20leave%20its%20premises%20do%20so%20with%20a%20promise%20to%20return.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20birth%20of%20a%20heritage%20getaway%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENumerous%20homestays%20%E2%80%94%20both%20legal%20and%20illegal%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F280532%2Fchildhood-friends-convert-grandmothers-house-into-eco-friendly-homestay-maharashtra%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edot%20the%20landscape%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20Western%20Ghats%20today%2C%20but%20the%20couple%20was%20intent%20on%20making%20theirs%20in%20accordance%20with%20rules%20and%20legal%20sanctions.%20They%20spent%20the%20next%20three%20years%20in%20talks%20with%20the%20tourism%20board%20of%20the%20state.%20They%20also%20visited%20tourism%20fairs%20across%20India%20to%20learn%20firsthand%20how%20to%20set%20up%20a%20homestay%20and%20everything%20else%20it%20entailed.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fupl