%80%9CApart%20from%20Science%20and%20Mathematics%2C%20we%20are%20also%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F326816%2Frennis-joseph-started-ignis-careers-to-help-children-learn-english-pursue-higher-education%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etaught%20English%20%3C%2Fa%3Efrom%20YouTube.%20When%20I%20go%20back%20home%2C%20I%20show%20my%20parents%20that%20I%20can%20speak%20English%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds%2C%20noting%20that%20she%20aspires%20to%20be%20a%20doctor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiya%20is%20part%20of%20a%20cohort%20of%201%20lakh%20students%20under%20Muskaan%20Dreams%2C%20whose%20founder%20Abhishek%20Dubey%20is%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20make%20learning%20in%20government%20schools%20fun.%20He%20does%20so%20through%20a%20number%20of%20interventions%2C%20including%20teaching%20children%20NCERT%20syllabus%20via%20animations%20and%20fun%20videos.%20The%20non-profit%20aims%20to%20bridge%20the%20digital%20gap%20in%20transforming%20education%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F178695%2Fbengaluru-tactile-books-graphics-education-disability-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emarginalised%20children%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20rural%20communities%20without%20the%20burden%20of%20an%20additional%20fee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-1-1692363836.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Abhishek%20has%20introduced%20a%20number%20of%20interventions%2C%20including%20teaching%20children%20NCERT%20syllabus%20via%20animations%20and%20fun%20videos.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-1-1692363836.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%